FBIS4-39109 "drsov108_r_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-108 Daily Report 5 Jun 1994 Azerbaijan Armenians Reportedly Preparing New Offensive Armenians Reportedly Preparing New Offensive NC0506194194 Baku TURAN in English 1703 GMT 5 Jun 94 NC0506194194 Baku TURAN English BFN [Text] Baku (June 4) TURAN -- According to Azerbaijan's Defense Ministry a relative calm is observed along the front line. At the same time, having crossed the state border of Azerbaijan and having started a new offensive towards Kemerli (Kazakh region of Azerbaijan) Armenian forces in result of fights mastered height Melicli, which is of strategical importance. Turan was told by local sources that remaining loyal to cease fire agreement Azerbaijan did not answered to this military actions of Armenia. Military sources told Turan that Armenian Military forces continue to gather military hardware and soldiers on the north front.
